<body>
    <h1>Task 22 - RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 local-id=3D"fe76b21b2cc2" id=3D"Task22-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"590ebdb30fa4" id=3D"Task22-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h3>
<p local-id=3D"38c5eeff75db">This Requirement Analysis Document (RAD) defin=
es the functional and non-functional requirements for setting up a self-hos=
ted GitLab Community Edition (CE) server on an AWS EC2 instance and deployi=
ng a Flask Hello World application to a repository hosted on it. This docum=
ent is intended for DevOps interns, project leads, and technical reviewers =
at ABC Technologies.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"bc7ef369b597" id=3D"Task22-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8bf89e7aa303">This document covers:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f7e8b699fa15">Provisioning and configuring a GitLab CE serve=
r on an EC2 instance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f62b7fe31c1b">Creating a GitLab project/repository for a Fla=
sk application</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"83f78d28d2ff">Developing a basic Flask Hello World applicati=
on</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1417301248e9">Pushing application code from a local/server e=
nvironment to the GitLab CE repository</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f1ed6378df48">Validating the entire setup end-to-end</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9843eb4ef03c">Out of Scope:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5b824ba852c4">CI/CD pipeline configuration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a7bec638ce3c">Production-grade deployment of the Flask app</=
p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5e116aa6bda2">GitLab EE (Enterprise Edition) features</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"426d43a351d6">Multi-node GitLab HA setup</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"f40dff1d6cc2" id=3D"Task22-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h3>
