<h3 local-id=3D"b985aaf31d96" id=3D"Task22-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d3d1d51a455b">GitLab CE Official Documentation: <a class=3D"=
external-link" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://docs.gitlab.=
com/ee/install/" rel=3D"nofollow">https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/install/</a></=
p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"06e645258e2f">Flask Official Documentation: <a class=3D"exte=
rnal-link" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://flask.palletspro=
jects.com/" rel=3D"nofollow">https://flask.palletsprojects.com/</a></p></li=
>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fbe454675fc8">AWS EC2 Documentation: <a class=3D"external-li=
nk" href=3D"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ec2/" rel=3D"nofollow">https://docs=
.aws.amazon.com/ec2/</a></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9d6f522a2d7f">Git Official Documentation: <a class=3D"extern=
al-link" href=3D"https://git-scm.com/doc" rel=3D"nofollow">https://git-scm.=
com/doc</a></p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fb324505e530">ABC Technologies Internal DevOps Runbook (if a=
pplicable)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"25183a99a878" id=3D"Task22-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
3>
<p local-id=3D"c6145895bf12">This document is structured as follows:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b16245345d08">Section 2 provides a project overview includin=
g objectives, business goals, background, and constraints.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"eb1b0e26fbdb">Section 3 details the functional requirements =
through use cases and a use case diagram.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d3dbc9a5de18">Section 4 describes the non-functional require=
ments including performance, security, and reliability.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a2ca39625b28">Section 5 covers assumptions and dependencies.=
</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"095bfed60daf">Section 6 outlines the risk analysis.</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"39467132be1c">Section 7 provides a glossary of key terms.</p=
></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ac338af505d7">Section 8 contains appendices with supplementa=
ry material.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"c08b74a3edfe" id=3D"Task22-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"dff6fe522acc" id=3D"Task22-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9cdc6aff5be4">Deploy a fully functional GitLab CE server on =
an AWS EC2 instance accessible via a browser</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c1c30cb3ef79">Configure the GitLab instance for admin access=
 and basic repository management</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"341457458ce0">Create a dedicated project/repository for the =
Flask Hello World application</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"efea4aac9491">Push functional Flask Hello World source code =
to the GitLab CE repository</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a7aa0628f71a">Validate Git-based version control workflows o=
n the self-hosted GitLab instance</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"7f15f468dfd2" id=3D"Task22-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4e2188594610">Establish internal source code management infr=
astructure independent of third-party platforms (e.g., GitHub, Bitbucket)</=
p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e6aefb649ce1">Enable ABC Technologies to maintain full owner=
ship and control over its codebase</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5fba93982f44">Provide the development team with a collaborat=
ive platform for code review, version control, and project management</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d75b4b6bfa4f">Build foundational DevOps knowledge within the=
 intern team through hands-on deployment tasks</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"98404afff59e">Reduce external dependency and potential licen=
sing costs by adopting an open-source VCS platform</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"a3c68ba4d402" id=3D"Task22-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h3>
<p local-id=3D"fa3dac1ba1d4">ABC Technologies currently lacks a self-hosted=
 version control system. The development team relies on external platforms,=
 which poses data sovereignty and security concerns. To address this, the o=
rganization has decided to evaluate GitLab CE as an internal code managemen=
t solution. This task serves as a proof of concept (PoC) where a DevOps int=
ern will set up the environment, validate its functionality by pushing a si=
mple Flask application, and document the process for the wider team.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"193a5c72b287" id=3D"Task22-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a4=
223f29-8ef6-45d3-8411-0ca146e67d3f" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c13777746345">Constraint Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1d031d035744">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"70f02326b562">Time</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eff810d27599">The entire task must be completed within 3 hou=
rs</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4b2edf351202">Budget</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"910cbba28527">Use of free-tier or minimal-cost AWS EC2 insta=
nce (t2.medium or t3.medium recommended for GitLab)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"891bcf15cded">Technology</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b8c756f7c2d7">GitLab Community Edition only (not Enterprise =
Edition)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"648ad699e684">Platform</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1378b983742d">AWS EC2 as the hosting environment</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9b164bf9b08b">OS</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ed8d4f4e2ae">Ubuntu 20.04 LTS or 22.04 LTS on the EC2 insta=
nce</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8581055f0267">Network</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4bd38bba68f2">EC2 Security Group must allow ports 22 (SSH), =
80 (HTTP), 443 (HTTPS)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c9d938273c73">Access</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"09e2c6f10152">Admin credentials must be securely managed; de=
fault root password must be changed</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"55336dfacc9a" id=3D"Task22-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"719c15164729" id=3D"Task22-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h3><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-cente=
r-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedde=
d-image image-center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (18)-20260327-090950.p=
ng" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"a2e6188a2027597ec6c261b3250b1eceb=
78c7733c494e36a04e71fc54a2d5442" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian=
