<h3 local-id=3D"df1c0aecb888" id=3D"Task22-RAD-6.2RiskMitigation">6.2 Risk =
Mitigation</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"df=
736eef-dc98-468e-9b98-18440927640d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"41afc5ca6ce7">Risk ID</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"32d8ffd81b7e">Mitigation Strategy</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a39fc4149859">R1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"192ab76732cf">Use a t2.medium or t3.medium instance (minimum=
 4 GB RAM) as recommended by GitLab CE system requirements</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a73f72e0ca94">R2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e2091ddd7a47">Verify Security Group rules before and after G=
itLab installation; ensure ports 22, 80, and 443 are open</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bb492d6f3273">R3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d6d5d5267f7d">Immediately retrieve the initial root password=
 from <code>/etc/gitlab/initial_root_password</code> right after installati=
on and change it</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ddfac4d4388f">R4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"804a7d4dd85c">Generate and use a Personal Access Token from =
GitLab instead of using the root password for Git operations; test authenti=
cation before code push</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"346d409f6612">R5</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"557c157d91a1">Follow a structured step-by-step approach; use=
 the official GitLab CE installation script to minimize manual steps</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"eb768534614e">R6</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d0bed8d80ada">Assign an Elastic IP (EIP) to the EC2 instance=
 to maintain a static public IP; update <code>external_url</code> in <code>=
/etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb</code> if IP changes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2b68f4d0f1d4">R7</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fa9cf1464c58">Add the local machine's SSH public key to GitL=
ab under User Settings &gt; SSH Keys before attempting SSH-based Git operat=
ions</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9621033dd71e">R8</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bfb77eeca2f8">Use <code>git push -u origin HEAD</code> to pu=
sh the current branch regardless of its name; or explicitly rename to <code=
>main</code> using <code>git branch -M main</code></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"2e336e8e8036" id=3D"Task22-RAD-7.Glossary">7. Glossary</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"dc=
f2f619-8e59-48b0-a0f9-2564ac11f69d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b13850c9bd7a">Term</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3af141ade227">Definition</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"92ba3fd0f27d">GitLab CE</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b2bd3707c25e">Community Edition of GitLab =E2=80=94 a free, =
open-source, self-hosted Git repository management platform</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2cdcce15b058">GitLab EE</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0633b183268a">Enterprise Edition of GitLab =E2=80=94 a paid =
version with advanced features</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ae99e007342">GitHub</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7ce213076d85">A cloud-based Git repository hosting service o=
wned by Microsoft</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"12cc6644141f">Jenkins</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"36e2fd7f8a22">An open-source automation server used for CI/C=
D pipeline implementation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1e06cd937e34">Flask</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4447e24115cc">A micro web framework written in Python, desig=
ned for simplicity and flexibility</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"beb07886e01d">EC2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"281a073f9840">Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud =E2=80=94 a web s=
ervice providing scalable virtual servers in the AWS cloud</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f6ebf131fcd1">Security Group</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"05c36e143d8f">A virtual firewall in AWS that controls inboun=
d and outbound traffic to EC2 instances</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4e5967b05555">SSH</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"79ecb5b2d260">Secure Shell =E2=80=94 a cryptographic network=
 protocol for secure communication between systems</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a110468e946a">PAT</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e33fafd7f7f9">Personal Access Token =E2=80=94 a token used t=
o authenticate against GitLab APIs and Git operations instead of a password=
</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"72f931099758">Git Remote</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f2a4e1f19eb0">A reference to a remote Git repository URL con=
figured in a local Git repository</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"53a8e155f4fc">Repository</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1cd4f38c30c0">A storage structure containing all project fil=
es and version history managed by Git</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"65bf9b6a1db2">Commit</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"639cdbf2423e">A snapshot of changes saved to a Git repositor=
y at a specific point in time</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"02624376cbed">Push</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6c40c18512a4">The Git operation of uploading local commits t=
o a remote repository</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c5c950ed7369">Clone</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b7cc0d85b99">The Git operation of downloading a remote repo=
sitory to a local machine</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ba747c9d5d40">Reconfigure</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a5b0260b8ba2">A GitLab-specific command (<code>gitlab-ctl re=
configure</code>) that applies changes to the GitLab configuration file</p>=
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fdd3940146b9">PoC</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6e01b92585ca">Proof of Concept =E2=80=94 a demonstration to =
verify feasibility of a concept or approach</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"f8a4f6731846" id=3D"Task22-RAD-8.Appendices">8. Appendices<=
/h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"05a25eb4fa26" id=3D"Task22-RAD-AppendixA:GitLabCEInstallati=
onCommandReference">Appendix A: GitLab CE Installation Command Reference</h=
3>
<p local-id=3D"58583559b175">bash</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence"># Step =
1: Update system
sudo apt-get update &amp;&amp; sudo apt-get upgrade -y

# Step 2: Install dependencies
sudo apt-get install -y curl ca-certificates postfix

# Step 3: Add GitLab CE package repository
curl https://packages.gitlab.com/install/repositories/gitlab/gitlab-ce/scri=
pt.deb.sh | sudo bash

# Step 4: Install GitLab CE with external URL
sudo EXTERNAL_URL=3D"http://&lt;EC2-PUBLIC-IP&gt;" apt-get install gitlab-c=
e

# Step 5: Reconfigure
sudo gitlab-ctl reconfigure

# Step 6: Check status
sudo gitlab-ctl status

# Step 7: Get initial root password
sudo cat /etc/gitlab/initial_root_password</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"54146f2e6653" id=3D"Task22-RAD-AppendixB:FlaskHelloWorldApp=
licationFiles">Appendix B: Flask Hello World Application Files</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e4a560fcacd7"><strong>app.py</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"e86d55b145f3">python</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">from fl=
ask import Flask
app =3D Flask(__name__)

@app.route('/')
def hello():
    return 'Hello World'

if __name__ =3D=3D '__main__':
    app.run(debug=3DTrue)
```

**requirements.txt**
```
flask</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"8898b17eb050" id=3D"Task22-RAD-AppendixC:GitCommandsforCode=
Push">Appendix C: Git Commands for Code Push</h3>
<p local-id=3D"17bcf4d5c004">bash</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence"># Initi=
alize local repo
git init

# Configure user
git config user.name "Your Name"
git config user.email "your@email.com"

# Stage and commit
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: Flask Hello World app"

# Add GitLab CE remote
git remote add origin http://&lt;EC2-PUBLIC-IP&gt;/root/flask-hello-world.g=
it

# Push code
git push -u origin main</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"967b47ac1574" id=3D"Task22-RAD-AppendixD:DifferenceBetweenG=
itLab,GitHub,andJenkins">Appendix D: Difference Between GitLab, GitHub, and=
 Jenkins</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"da=
e597f1-c234-4413-be27-abb9853031f9" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"001c46ef719d">Feature</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"968d37258d50">GitLab</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7f67e0222bc0">GitHub</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1b1eaf303622">Jenkins</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b30ebf4ca223">Primary Purpose</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fbc571116572">Self-hosted or cloud Git repository management=
 with built-in CI/CD</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"83c2bb3c200f">Cloud-based Git repository hosting and collabo=
ration</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2a21a752152b">Open-source CI/CD automation server</p></td>
</tr>
